DSJobDef.name: P_TB_ODCMS_Z_CAMP_EXCLD_CUST_01

Property.valueExpression:
SELECT CAMP_ID AS CMPGN_ID
     , NODE_ID AS CMPGN_NODE_ID
     , IFNULL(STEP_CD,'~') AS CMPGN_STEP_CD
     , IFNULL(POLICY_CD,'~') AS CUST_CNTT_PLCY_CD
     , MBR_NO AS DPSTR_CUST_NO
     , CAMP_EXEC_NO AS CMPGN_EXEC_TMS
     , COMPA_YN AS CTGRP_YN
     , DATE_FORMAT(LOAD_DTTM,'%Y%m%d%h%i%s') AS LOAD_DTM
     , IFNULL(EXCLL_CUST_GRDE_SMCLS_CD,'~') AS EXCLL_CUST_GRDE_SMCLS_CD
     , IFNULL(CUST_EVL_GRDE_CD,'~') AS CUST_EVL_GRDE_CD
     , IFNULL(MEMB_SEX_CL_CD,'~') AS MEMB_SEX_CL_CD
     , IFNULL(AGE_MDCLS_CD,'~') AS AGE_MDCLS_CD
     , SCSS_DMCY_YN AS SCSS_DMCY_YN
     , DPSTR_EXSF_YN AS DPSTR_EXSF_YN
     , COWK_YN AS COWK_YN
     , FGNR_YN AS FGNR_YN
     , DPSTR_APP_PUSH_AGR_YN AS DPSTR_APP_PUSH_AGR_YN
     , SMS_RCV_AGR_YN AS SMS_RCV_AGR_YN
     , REPLACE( EMAIL_RCV_AGR_YN, char( 0 ), '' ) AS EMAIL_RCV_AGR_YN
     , DM_RCV_AGR_YN AS MEMB_DM_RCV_AGR_YN
     , FTDG_YN AS CHNL_FTDG_YN
     , FAN_YN AS FAN_YN
 FROM #P_DB_CMS.$S_CMS_SCM#.Z_CAMP_EXCLD_CUST
WHERE LOAD_DTTM >= CAST( '#$S_FROM_YMD#' as DATETIME )
  AND LOAD_DTTM < DATE_ADD(CAST( '#$S_TO_YMD#' as DATETIME ),INTERVAL 1 DAY)
